Package: usensys
Title: United States ENergy SYStem optimization model (USENSYS)
Version: 0.0.2.9001
Date: 2024-10-15
Authors@R: 
    person("Oleg", "Lugovoy", 
          email = "usensys@optimalsolution.dev", 
          role = c("aut", "cre"), 
          comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5546-9875"))
Description: R interface to the open source United States ENergy SYStem (USENSYS) 
             optimization model with alternative regional configuration, technological options, 
             and data sources. The package provides functions to choose the 
             model configuration and the data from the list of available options, 
             design technologies, processes, policies, and define scenarios,
             run the model, store and analyze the results. The model is based on
             the energyRt package and uses Python/Pyomo or Julia/JuMP or GAMS as
             the optimization solver. 
URL: https://www.usensys.org; https://github.com/usensys/usensys
BugReports: https://github.com/usensys/usensys/issues
